      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
        <div class="bg-greenels/10 border-l-4 border-greenels rounded-lg p-6 hover:bg-greenels/20 transition">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-graytext mb-2">üéì Digital Humanities</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-graytext/80">Computational methods in philosophy and cultural studies.</p>
