            Art, design, and personal creative projects. Creating allows me to experiment with new ideas, express myself visually, and push boundaries across different mediums.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="rounded-xl overflow-hidden border-2 border-greenels/40 hover:border-blueels transition md:order-1">
